Improvements to the bucket store. - moved from internal to a package to allow external use - use of btree instead of map in kvmemstore (renamed to kvbtree) - improved benchmark tests - fixed some race conditions in test cases - add methods to iterate in bulk NextN, PrevN

Changed ThingID to ThingAddr, eg include publisher - A thing publishes using the ThingID - A subscriber receives the ThingAddr and uses it to get info. - Malicious devices cannot spoof values of other things. - Added capnp support for pubsub.
